  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a unique presentation of pseudo-Cushing's syndrome caused by pheochromocytoma, which has not been previously reported in the literature.",
    "The mechanism involves catecholamine-induced hypermetabolism leading to HPA axis activation and a positive feedback loop involving cortisol and catecholamine production.",
    "Metyrapone treatment was effective in breaking the pathological feedback loop and reducing both cortisol and catecholamine levels."
  ]
